title: Episode 204: Go-Go Gadget Nipples (Feat. Shenseea)
itunes:title: Episode 204: Go-Go Gadget Nipples (Feat. Shenseea)
description:
Jamaican dancehall artist Shenseea joins the ladies of Lip Service this week. Shenseea explains to females why they shouldn't be insecure if your man is dancing with another women, her love for being tied up, what to do if a guy says 'I love you' when you don't, and much more. Enjoy!
